### Typography System

#### Font Families

- **Headings**: "Maven", sans-serif
- **Body Text**: "Montserrat", sans-serif
- **Code**: "Roboto Mono", monospace

#### Desktop Type Scale (Mobile-first approach)

```css
:root {
  /* Desktop sizes */
  --h1: 3rem; /* 48px */
  --h2: 2.25rem; /* 36px */
  --h3: 1.875rem; /* 30px */
  --h4: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
  --h5: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
  --h6: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
  --body-base: 1rem; /* 16px */
  --body-large: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
  --body-small: 0.875rem; /* 14px */
  --caption: 0.75rem; /* 12px */
}
```

#### Heading Hierarchy Rules

1. **One H1 per page** - main title only
2. **Don't skip heading levels** (H1 → H2 → H3, not H1 → H3)
3. **Mobile adjustments**: Reduce heading sizes proportionally

#### Text Colors by Element

- **Main Titles**: `#21211d` (Gray 900)
- **Subtitles**: `#42423e` (Gray 800)
- **Body Text**: `#61615d` (Gray 700)
- **Secondary Text**: `#75716d` (Gray 600)
- **Text on Dark Backgrounds**: `#fffbf7`
- **Links**: `#10763e`, hover: `#0e5e32`

### Layout & Spacing Guidelines

#### Section Backgrounds

- **Header/Footer**: `#003a33` with `#fffbf7` text
- **Main Content**: `#fffbf7` background
- **Card Backgrounds**: `#fffbf7` or `#f8f5f2` for hover
- **Testimonial Sections**: `#f8f5f2` background

